    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and she\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has plenty of life left for its next owner! It's been well-maintained and still looks great pulling into the driveway. Whether you need a reliable commuter or something for weekend trips, this beauty is ready to go. Drop me a message if you want to come see it!",
      "price": 32500.0,
