      "description": "This vehicle represents a distinguished balance of performance and value. Meticulously maintained and presenting in commendable condition, it offers a refined driving experience. Every mechanical component has been rigorously inspected to ensure continued reliability and roadworthiness. An excellent opportunity for the discerning driver seeking quality and longevity.",
      "price": 34800.0,
