      "description": "Hi there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride and it\u2019s looking for a new home! It\u2019s been super reliable and is still in really solid shape\u2014perfect for someone who wants a smooth drive without the 'brand new' price tag. It\u2019s been well-loved, kept clean, and is ready to hit the road with you today. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
